_aChangeLog.text: Fixed bonus boosters that wasn't working as intended in the bonus.

_sText:
Fixed bonus boosters, should work correctly now.

Hello again, this map is what was originally supposed to be a surf bonus for a map I lost motivation for, so I turned it into a bhop map. It's very fast paced and has a lot of twists and turns, but it's also the shortest map I have/will ever publish, I don't particularly like short maps myself but I know a lot of bhoppers enjoy running them, so have fun. For those wondering, map is about 20 seconds long for someone decent. I also added in a pretty fun bhop bonus that I don't think I've used in a bhop map before. PS some of screenshots are different because it was a different version, the map you see in the video is what the map looks like currently.
